-- Emirates Steel Industries First-Half Output Rises 45%, Sales Advances 30%
-- Vivian Salama
-- 2010-07-27T05:11:16Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-27/emirates-steel-industries-first-half-output-rises-45-sales-advances-30-.html

          
          
             Emirates Steel Industries PJSC said
first half output rose 45 percent and sales volume increased 30
percent, according to an e-mailed statement today.  
 The state-owned company sells most of its output in local
markets in the United Arab Emirates and exports of its main
products more than doubled, the company said. It exports to
countries like Jordan, Saudi Arabia, Kuwait, Oman, South Asia
and the Far East, it said.  
